<plot>It's snowed, and Donald is going sledding. Meanwhile, his newphews have built a snowman at the bottom of the hill. Donald aims his sled at their snowman and demolishes it so the boys get even by including a boulder in the bottom of their next snowman. This means war, so they retreat to opposing snow forts for battle.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?155903</url></doc>
